STATE
v.
Rocky Lee DeWALT. No. 261P08. Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 11, 2008. Carlos Mahoney, Durham, for Dewalt. Tom Horner, District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 26th day of June 2008 by State of NC to Dismiss Appeal:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference this the 11th day of December 2008."
